data.description: PRICE REDUCED....Situated on a corner lot, this captivating 4-bed, 2-bath home has vaulted ceilings and thoughtfully designed split floor plan. This home new AC and ductwork in 2021, doble insulation, a new roof in 2022, accordion shutters for storm protection, a new water heater in 2021, house repiping in 2021, Sprinkler system fed by a deep well. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an inviting breakfast bar. Recent interior paint enhances the welcoming open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining room, and the cozy eat-in kitchen area. Additional practical amenities include indoor laundry and a screened back porch overlooking the expansive fenced yard.  Centrally located with short drive to school, shopping, beaches and I95.
